bonus.title: Bet £10 Get £30 in free bets
bonus.text: New William Hill online customers only. Min. unit stake of £10/€10 at odds of 1.5 or greater. Only the “win” part from EW bets will count. Free bet terms, payment method & country restrictions apply. Free bets credited as 3 x £10/€10. Free bet stakes are not returned as part of the settlement of successful free bets. All Free Bets must be wagered within 30 days.
